ocwdMA.ExapWedTh.text = "All-pure one, you were present at the crucifixion of your Son. * You saw Him nailed and suspended * upon the cross, and Him dying. * Maternally you cried aloud, and shedding tears you said to Him, * \"What is this awful paradox, * that You who created all things * are crucified of Your own will?\""

